 ¬ Submit times
If you have a better time for any stage, and want it included in this table, simply send us the state.dat file and also the .rec file. Remember to tell us your nick, nationality, possible team and of course the time of the ride. Please compress the files you are about to send (zip format preferred). The deadline for the usual weekly Sunday update is Saturday 23:59 EET and the address to send the records to is pexi@moposite.com.

Note that if two or more persons get the same time, the one whose record came first will have the WR.
 ¬ Logos
If you want to have a team logo instead of plain link to teampage, send it with your record. Note that if your team already has one or more logos on the WR table, you don't need to send the logo with your new WRs. Maximum size for logos is 40*20 pixels and 4096 bytes. Logos must be in gif format.
